title: Muhammad Waheed wins PP-152 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N) candidate, Malik Muhammad Waheed has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-152, Lahore-VIII by securing 34,664 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was independent candidate, Noman Majeed who bagged 29,676 votes.
The votersâ€™ turnout remained 39.59%.
